---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="YardFavorites affiliate disclosure - how we earn money and our commitment to unbiased reviews."
>
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-lg">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2025</p>
      <h2>How We Earn Money</h2>
      <p>
        YardFavorites is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program,
        an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn
        advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
      </p>
      <p>
        This means we earn a small commission when you click our links and make a qualifying
        purchase on Amazon — at <strong>no extra cost to you</strong>.
      </p>
      <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate relationships <strong>never influence our reviews or rankings</strong>.
        Products are tested and ranked based on merit alone. We will always tell you
        if a product is not worth buying, regardless of commission rate.
      </p>
      <h2>Required Disclosures</h2>
      <p>
        In compliance with FTC guidelines, all product review pages contain clear
        disclosure that we may earn a commission from qualifying purchases.
      </p>
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>Contact us at <strong>hello@yardfavorites.com</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
